timeStamps.text: The movie opens up with a narrator explaining how there are people who remember their past lives called infinites
amongst them, two groups have vied for power, The Believers who protect the humans and The Nihilists who want to end all life on earth
we then see Heinrich Treadway trying to escape the authorities
he has got a scar on his stomach which he closes with the cars cigarette lighter
He and his associates, Abel and Leona talk about "the Egg,"
trying to avoid the cops, he decides to drive off a bridge,
jumping from his car in mid-air
